data.description: Cute Home in the Heart of Batesville, Has new flooring 2Bed, 2Bath with a large a kitchen, there are 3 other rooms that can be made into bedrooms or offices. This is a corner lot that you can access from the back or the front for extra parking such as boats or campers. There is a 12x16 storage shed and a carport for two cars. See Agent Remarks.
